- Misericordia Community Hospital Emergency Department - 16940 87 Ave, Edmonton 11 May 2014 - 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.

AHS declared an outbreak in the Calgary and Edmonton zones after several cases emerged in both areas, including an infant who was infected in Edmonton.

